com.b2international.commons.dynamic

Interface DynamicValue

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    DynamicList, DynamicMap
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractDynamicMap, AbstractDynamicValue, DynamicListImpl, DynamicMapImpl, DynamicValueImpl

    public interface DynamicValue
    Encapsulates an object of indeterminate type.

    • Field Summary

      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      static DynamicValue MISSING
      A shared instance representing a missing value.

      A shared instance wrapping the value null.

      • asBoolean

        boolean asBoolean()
        Returns the encapsulated object as a boolean primitive if it is an instance of Boolean, false otherwise. This method is the equivalent of calling as(Boolean.class, false).booleanValue().
        Returns:
        the object cast to boolean, or false

      • asBoolean

        boolean asBoolean(boolean defaultValue)
        Returns the encapsulated object as a boolean primitive if it is an instance of Boolean, defaultValue otherwise. This method is the equivalent of calling as(Boolean.class, defaultValue).booleanValue().
        Parameters:
        defaultValue - the boolean value to return if the encapsulated object is not an instance of Boolean
        Returns:
        the object cast to boolean, or defaultValue

      • asInt

        int asInt()
        Returns the encapsulated object as an integer primitive if it is an instance of Number, 0 otherwise. This method is the equivalent of calling as(Number.class, 0).intValue(). The operation may involve rounding or truncation.
        Returns:
        the object cast to int, or 0
